julius caesar is a 1953 epic metro-goldwyn-mayer film adaptation of the play by shakespeare , directed by joseph l. mankiewicz , who also wrote the uncredited screenplay , and produced by john houseman . the original music score is by miklós rózsa . the film stars marlon brando as mark antony , james mason as brutus , john gielgud as cassius , louis calhern as julius caesar , edmond o'brien as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , greer garson as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and deborah kerr as portia .